attributes.title: Theo Chocolate Bag
attributes.description:
Created on June 14, 2010 by Humblefactory on Sourcemap.org:

This bag is created as part of the Production Cycle project. It is sewn from waste bags used to ship coco beans from to Theo chocolate's factory in Fremont, and inner tubes from bicycle tires from Everybody Cycles on Boat Street.
